---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Privacy Policy - Protecting Your Ideas and Data" description="We value your trust. Read our privacy policy on how we handle data while helping turn your ideas into loved products.">





<!-- Privacy & Terms of Use – Paper Contract Style -->
<section class="py-16 md:py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-gradient-to-b from-teal-50 to-white">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-700 to-teal-900 text-white rounded-t-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
      <div class="p-8 md:p-12 text-center">
        <h1 class="
          text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl
          font-black tracking-tight leading-none
        ">
          Privacy & Terms of Use
        </h1>

        <p class="mt-4 text-lg md:text-xl font-medium opacity-90">
          Your trust matters. Please read carefully before using our website and actually purchasing any product on this website.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Paper-like content body -->
    <div class="
      bg-white shadow-xl rounded-b-2xl border border-gray-200 border-t-0
      p-6 md:p-10 lg:p-12
      prose prose-lg md:prose-xl max-w-none
      text-gray-800
    ">

      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-teal-800 mb-6 md:mb-8">
        1. Privacy Policy
      </h2>

      <p class="mb-6 md:mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. By using our website, you agree to the collection, use and storage of your information in accordance with this policy.
      </p>

      <p class="mb-6 md:mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        We collect information including your name, email, phone number and purchase details to improve our service and communicate with you effectively. We never sell your data to third parties and ensure all sensitive information is securely stored.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-teal-700 mb-4 md:mb-6">
        How we use your information
      </h3>

      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 md:pl-8 space-y-3 md:space-y-4 mb-8 md:mb-10">
        <li>To process orders and deliver products/services.</li>
        <li>To improve our website and service quality.</li>
        <li>To send important updates, promotions or support-related communications.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-teal-700 mb-4 md:mb-6">
        Data protection
      </h3>

      <p class="mb-8 md:mb-10 leading-relaxed">
        We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your personal data from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure or destruction.
      </p>

      <hr class="my-10 md:my-14 border-gray-300" />

      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-teal-800 mb-6 md:mb-8">
        2. Terms of Use
      </h2>

      <p class="mb-6 md:mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        By accessing or using our website, you agree to comply with these terms. You accept that all content is for informational purposes and we reserve the right to modify any terms without notice.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-teal-700 mb-4 md:mb-6">
        User responsibilities
      </h3>

      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 md:pl-8 space-y-3 md:space-y-4 mb-8 md:mb-10">
        <li>Providing accurate information when using our services.</li>
        <li>Respecting intellectual property rights.</li>
        <li>Not using the website for unlawful purposes.</li>
      </ul>

      <hr class="my-10 md:my-14 border-gray-300" />

      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-teal-800 mb-6 md:mb-8">
        3. Lay-by Policy
      </h2>

      <p class="mb-6 md:mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        We offer Lay-by purchasing to few selected product categories, to ensure fairness and transparency we have made contract sample available to all our beloved users <a href="/layby" class="text-teal-600 hover:text-teal-800 underline">see contract sample here</a>.
      </p>

      <hr class="my-10 md:my-14 border-gray-300" />

      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-teal-800 mb-6 md:mb-8">
        4. Delivery Policy
      </h2>

      <p class="mb-6 md:mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        We aim to deliver your products in the shortest time possible while maintaining quality and sustainability.
      </p>

      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 md:pl-8 space-y-3 md:space-y-4 mb-8 md:mb-10">
        <li><strong>Delivery Time:</strong> Typically 3–10 business days depending on product and location.</li>
        <li><strong>Shipping Costs:</strong> Calculated at checkout and communicated before payment.</li>
        <li><strong>Tracking:</strong> You will receive a tracking number to follow your order.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-teal-700 mb-4 md:mb-6">
        International Delivery
      </h3>

      <p class="mb-8 md:mb-10 leading-relaxed">
        We offer international delivery where possible. Customs duties, taxes and import fees may apply and are the responsibility of the buyer.
      </p>

      <hr class="my-10 md:my-14 border-gray-300" />

      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-teal-800 mb-6 md:mb-8">
        5. Returns & Refunds
      </h2>

      <p class="mb-6 md:mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        Your satisfaction is important. If you are not completely satisfied, we offer clear returns and refunds in accordance with the following:
      </p>

      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 md:pl-8 space-y-3 md:space-y-4 mb-8 md:mb-10">
        <li><strong>Return Period:</strong> You have 14 days from the date of delivery to request a return.</li>
        <li><strong>Condition:</strong> Products must be returned in original condition, unused and with packaging intact.</li>
        <li><strong>Refund Process:</strong> Once we receive and inspect the item, refunds will be processed within 7 business days.</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="italic text-gray-600 mb-8 md:mb-10">
        Custom-made or personalized products cannot be returned unless defective.
      </p>

      <hr class="my-10 md:my-14 border-gray-300" />

      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-teal-800 mb-6 md:mb-8">
        6. Need Clarification?
      </h2>

      <p class="mb-8 md:mb-10 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed">
        If you don't fully understand any part of these terms or our policies before proceeding to use the site or make a purchase, we encourage you to contact us. Your clarity and confidence matter to us.
      </p>

      <!-- CTA Button -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="
            inline-block bg-teal-700 hover:bg-teal-800
            text-white font-bold px-10 py-5 rounded-xl
            text-lg md:text-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl
            transition-all duration-300
          "
        >
          Go to Contact Page →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>



</MainLayout>
